lil-durk-figure.name: Lil Durk 10-inch Resin Figure
lil-durk-figure.description:
The Lil Durk 10-inch Resin Figure is a premium collectible made for true fans. Crafted from high-quality resin, this figure features detailed sculpting and a solid, display-ready build.

Designed to capture Lil Durk's signature style and presence, it's the perfect piece for shelves, desks, or display cases.

 10-inch tall resin figure
 High-quality, durable build
 Detailed design and finish
 Limited edition collectible
